We first implement experiments on ResNets2. The results are shown in Table 2. All these models are trained only on the ImageNet-1K training set and report their accuracy on the validation set. We mainly compare RA-Net with ResNet, SE-Net, and CBAM. As shown in Table 2, we analyze the results from the following perspectives, including parameters, FLOPs, Top-1, and Top-5 accuracy. FLOPs are obtained when the input size is \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
